# Tests

- Run `.venv/bin/pytest -q` from the repo root (venv).
- Fake clients should implement only the methods the code under test calls (see `tests/test_regime_history.py`, `tests/test_pages.py`).
- Use `app.models.DataResult` where the real client returns `DataResult`.
- Avoid live network in unit tests unless explicitly marked or isolated.
